# If data folder has very large raw data, usually we exclude it, but we need metadata.
# The prompt says "Keep all source code, configuration files, documentation, reports, and the frozen dataset metadata required to reproduce the project."
# Our dataset_v0 is processed and frozen. We'll commit data/processed/dataset_v0/ and data/splits/
# We'll ignore raw huggingface caches or raw data if any.
data/raw/*
!data/raw/bipia
data/generated/

